        <mxCell id="19" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;arcSize=5;" value="&lt;b&gt;Step 3 — extract_speed_bands.py&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; &lt;b&gt;Speed bands:&lt;/b&gt; lower_band = P10(speed), upper_band = P90(speed) per cluster&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; &lt;b&gt;Medoid extraction:&lt;/b&gt; i* = argmin &amp;#8214;x&lt;sub&gt;i&lt;/sub&gt; &amp;minus; &amp;mu;&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;&amp;#8214; &amp;nbsp;(actual record nearest centroid)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; &lt;b&gt;Per-LinkID validation:&lt;/b&gt; flag if mean speed deviates &amp;gt; 15 km/h&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;from cluster band midpoint &amp;nbsp;(spatial outlier diagnostic)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Append cluster_id, lower_band, upper_band to original dataset" vertex="1">
